attorneys: Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Arizona, Division Two dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
casebody.head_matter:
Victor PIANKA, petitioner,
v.
ARIZONA.
No. 16-6461.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 12, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Arizona, Division Two dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
